<title>
Rastavljanje i sastavljanje diferencijala
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5206010">Demontaža i montaža jedinice ručnog mjenjača</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5206014">Rastavljanje i sastavljanje petog stupnja prijenosa</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5206015">Rastavljanje i sastavljanje sklopa ručnog mjenjača</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5206024">Komponente diferencijala</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5206025001">
<title>
Rastavljanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Specijalnim alatom uklonite lijevi ležaj (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B036">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-65135">
09913-65135
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B037">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-85230">
09913-85230
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I6RS0E520012.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.438mm" ver = "01" gw = "92" gh = "107"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite desni ležaj na isti način kao u 1. koraku.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Kućište diferencijala (1) poduprite škripcem s mekanim čeljustima.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite vijke zadnjeg zupčanika i uklonite zadnji zupčanik.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite zatik vratila zupčanika diferencijala upotrebom specijalnog alata i čekića, a zatim rastavite dijelove komponente.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B038">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-85811">
09922-85811
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I6RS0E520013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.106mm" ver = "01" gw = "107" gh = "117"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
